"{\"uid\": \"wsus1023.iheart.com-featured-steve-andrews-content-2024-06-06-tomorrows-special-olympics-torch-run-will-complicate-the-morning-commute\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Want to know more about Steve Andrews?\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 38, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 24, \"end\": 37, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Andrews\", \"score\": 0.9999740507500445, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Steve Andrews\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Andrews\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Andrews\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Get his official bio, social pages and more!Full Bio  This year's Special Olympics Torch Run will take place tomorrow in communities across New Jersey.\", \"from\": 39, \"to\": 190, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 105, \"end\": 121, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999956799, \"rank\": 4.299758797276815e-12, \"text\": \"Special Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 179, \"end\": 189, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Jersey\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 1.3430593228104927e-13, \"text\": \"New Jersey\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Jersey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Jersey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This year more than 3.000 law enforcement officers will be running.\", \"from\": 191, \"to\": 258, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This annual event raises millions of dollars for Special Olympics every year.\", \"from\": 259, \"to\": 336, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Unfortunately, the traffic delays the torch run causes are expected to be made worse by this week's Route 15 bridge closure.\", \"from\": 337, \"to\": 461, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All we can do is give you the times the torch run will be traveling along Sussex County Roads.\", \"from\": 462, \"to\": 556, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So you can plan ahead.\", \"from\": 557, \"to\": 579, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At 6 o'clock tomorrow morning the first leg of the run will begin at the Wantage Municipal Building and proceed south along Route 23 reaching Hamburg around 7:10.\", \"from\": 581, \"to\": 743, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 654, \"end\": 661, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wantage\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 7.124432365229138e-13, \"text\": \"Wantage\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wantage\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wantage\"}, {\"begin\": 662, \"end\": 680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manhattan_Municipal_Building\", \"score\": 0.7644233454119899, \"rank\": 0.3070467839227031, \"text\": \"Municipal Building\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manhattan_Municipal_Building\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manhattan_Municipal_Building\"}, {\"begin\": 723, \"end\": 730, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamburg\", \"score\": 0.9969592256943047, \"rank\": 0.0021542016149100067, \"text\": \"Hamburg\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamburg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamburg\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A second leg of the run will begin at Mountain Creek at 6:40.\", \"from\": 744, \"to\": 805, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 782, \"end\": 796, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mountain_Creek\", \"score\": 0.9999999999988631, \"rank\": 7.491876165679237e-13, \"text\": \"Mountain Creek\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mountain_Creek\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mountain_Creek\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then proceed south along Route 94 into Hamburg.\", \"from\": 806, \"to\": 853, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 845, \"end\": 852, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamburg\", \"score\": 0.9969592256943047, \"rank\": 0.0021542016149100067, \"text\": \"Hamburg\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamburg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamburg\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Where it will join the first leg.\", \"from\": 854, \"to\": 887, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All of the runners will then travel south on Route 23.\", \"from\": 888, \"to\": 942, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Then make a right turn onto Route 517 and travel south into Sparta.\", \"from\": 943, \"to\": 1010, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1003, \"end\": 1009, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sparta\", \"score\": 0.9999367249364866, \"rank\": 6.327906758494716e-05, \"text\": \"Sparta\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sparta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sparta\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In Sparta the runners will turn left onto Route 620.\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1063, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1014, \"end\": 1020, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sparta\", \"score\": 0.9999367249364866, \"rank\": 6.327906758494716e-05, \"text\": \"Sparta\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sparta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sparta\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then onto Route 181 south.\", \"from\": 1064, \"to\": 1090, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Then take Route 605 into Hopatcong.\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1126, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This leg of the run that starts in Sussex County comes to an end in Somerville around 3:30 PM.\", \"from\": 1128, \"to\": 1222, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1163, \"end\": 1176, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sussex_County_Cricket_Club\", \"score\": 0.9999999996502993, \"rank\": 2.545295287803307e-10, \"text\": \"Sussex County\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\